  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goblins of Elderstone brings a unique and chaotic twist to the city-building genre - it’s a Goblin Tribe Simulator! Are you ready to embrace the chaos of goblin life? As the leader of a goblin tribe, it's up to you to build, manage, and defend your village against all odds and even the goblins themselves. See to their growing needs to keep them from rioting and make sure the pantheon of gods is appeased to succeed. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Free-form City Building</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/c534c0af604dd50a2f1f341cdbbb2419.poster.avif?t=1772096175\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/c534c0af604dd50a2f1f341cdbbb2419.webm?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/c534c0af604dd50a2f1f341cdbbb2419.mp4?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goblins don’t much like orderly straight lines, so there’s absolutely no way they’ll use a grid when building. They are rebellious but creative. As a result, buildings go up wherever desired, but neat little pathways and bridges will always be built alongside them to ensure they’re properly connected.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Assign your Goblins</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/a21d49ec37c4c50130f4353c6524c922.poster.avif?t=1772096175\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/a21d49ec37c4c50130f4353c6524c922.webm?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/a21d49ec37c4c50130f4353c6524c922.mp4?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 30 different resources that can be gathered, crafted, traded, or stolen, your goblins will always have plenty of work to do. Assign goblins to jobs based on their personal traits - good or bad - and employ Enforcers to keep them in line!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survive the harsh winters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/68e48fde672177715d4de42e8a995bfc.poster.avif?t=1772096175\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/68e48fde672177715d4de42e8a995bfc.webm?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/68e48fde672177715d4de42e8a995bfc.mp4?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Danger lurks around every corner. Defend your tribe from roaming monsters, skeletons, and other enemies by assigning guard goblins, hiring wandering heroes, and appealing to the gods for help. And if that doesn't cut it, your goblins will be more than happy to hide indoors until the threat passes! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore and Raid </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/dea8414e1f5abd34a8cada8631e11f0f.poster.avif?t=1772096175\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/dea8414e1f5abd34a8cada8631e11f0f.webm?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/dea8414e1f5abd34a8cada8631e11f0f.mp4?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Send your goblins to gather loot all over Elderstone with <strong>Raids</strong>, a brand-new system replacing the old Treks. Raids are punchier, faster, and far more connected to your village’s survival.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build your ultimate Tribe!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/95a34148928b6be7b83864b27241743d.poster.avif?t=1772096175\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/95a34148928b6be7b83864b27241743d.webm?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/95a34148928b6be7b83864b27241743d.mp4?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Marvel as your village grows and expands. There are many unique tales to unravel in this twisted land, and you will be asked to make difficult choices throughout your reign that will either help or hinder your progress.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Rule the Chaos!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/5656a88ead38ae27bd4de7601e762580.poster.avif?t=1772096175\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/5656a88ead38ae27bd4de7601e762580.webm?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/5656a88ead38ae27bd4de7601e762580.mp4?t=1772096175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goblins aren’t really the patient, caring type. They’re better at setting fire to farms than actually growing anything. As your tribe expands, you will need to fulfill your goblins' needs and wants to ensure they survive and - hopefully - thrive! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>➥ Join the Tribe on Discord</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/693580/extras/9717b380407e46820408900e03591bd2.avif?t=1772096175\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p>",
